name: Vice Principals
overview: The story of a high school and the people who almost run it, the vice principals.
tagline: Someone’s got to teach this school a lesson.

episodes.name: The Principal
episodes.overview: When the principal of a high school retires, his two vice principals go to extremes to land the vacant job.

episodes.name: A Trusty Steed
episodes.overview: Gamby and Russell end up invading Dr. Brown's private space and the vice principals are surprised by a school evaluator.

episodes.name: The Field Trip
episodes.overview: Gamby looks to impress Amanda on a field trip organized by Mr. Hayden, a good-guy history teacher.

episodes.name: Run for the Money
episodes.overview: Gamby and Russell eye a homecoming football game as a way to further break Dr. Brown’s spirit.

episodes.name: Circles
episodes.overview: Dr. Brown orders Gamby to lighten up on discipline; Russell copes with a disruptive neighbor.

episodes.name: The Foundation of Learning
episodes.overview: Amanda makes a deal with Gamby, while Dr. Brown takes a veteran teacher to task over a shipment of missing books.

episodes.name: The Good Book
episodes.overview: Gamby bonds with Amanda during teacher workday; Russell’s patience is tested; Dr. Brown deals with the sudden appearance of her ex-husband, Dascious.

episodes.name: Gin
episodes.overview: Gamby and Russell look to finish what they started; Gamby confronts Amanda about her relationship with Hayden.

episodes.name: End of the Line
episodes.overview: Gamby and Russell play their end game with Dr. Brown.

episodes.name: Tiger Town
episodes.overview: Recovering from his wounds, Gamby returns to a dramatically changed North Jackson High.

episodes.name: Slaughter
episodes.overview: Gamby fingers a suspect, with Dayshawn’s help. Russell tests out a kindness strategy at school.

episodes.name: The King
episodes.overview: Gamby’s search for his shooter leads him into a novelist’s graduate-school class. Russell’s ire is fueled by an unflattering caricature.

episodes.name: Think Change
episodes.overview: A death in Russell’s family forces Gamby to step up to the plate as North Jackson’s acting principal.

episodes.name: A Compassionate Man
episodes.overview: Russell’s birthday bash is marred by a revelation about his wife’s college boyfriend.

episodes.name: The Most Popular Boy
episodes.overview: A plot to sabotage a standardized test jeopardizes Russell’s job as Gamby is caught in the middle.

episodes.name: Spring Break
episodes.overview: Gamby gets unexpected company on spring break; Amanda is illuminated during a writer’s retreat.

episodes.name: Venetian Nights
episodes.overview: Tensions between Gamby and Russell come to a head as prom night approaches.

episodes.name: The Union of the Wizard & The Warrior
episodes.overview: The school year comes to a startling end.
